我在给学生上课的时候
When I am giving lessons to students.

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:28.666
wǒ wèn tā nǐ xǐhuan chī zhōngguócài ma
我问他你喜欢吃中国菜吗
I ask him, do you like eating Chinese food?

00:04:28.700 --> 00:04:30.533
tā shuō xǐhuan
他说喜欢
He says, "like."

00:04:30.533 --> 00:04:32.266
nà nǐ juéde zhège yǒu shénme wèntí ma
那你觉得这个有什么问题吗
Then do you think there is any problem with this?

00:04:32.266 --> 00:04:34.833
rúguǒ shì yuànyì "shuō" de xuésheng
如果是愿意"说"的学生
If it is a student willing to "speak."

00:04:34.866 --> 00:04:36.866
tā bù zhǐshì shuō xǐhuan
他不只是说喜欢
He doesn't just say "like."

00:04:36.866 --> 00:04:38.233
wǒ yǒu yìxiē qiàopíde xuésheng
我有一些俏皮的学生
I have some witty students.

00:04:38.233 --> 00:04:40.133
jiùshì hěn ài shuō de xuésheng
就是很爱说的学生
Students who love to speak.

00:04:40.166 --> 00:04:41.700
rúguǒ wǒ zhèyàng wèntā dehuà
如果我这样问他的话
If I ask him like this.

00:04:41.733 --> 00:04:43.400
nǐ xǐhuan chī zhōngguócài ma
你喜欢吃中国菜吗
Do you like eating Chinese food?

00:04:43.400 --> 00:04:44.733
tā huì shuō lǎoshī
他会说老师
He will say, "Teacher."

00:04:44.733 --> 00:04:46.700
nǐ zhǐde nǎr de zhōngguócài
你指的哪儿的中国菜
Which place's Chinese food are you referring to?

00:04:46.766 --> 00:04:48.033
bǐrúshuō sìchuān de
比如说四川的
For example, Sichuan's.

00:04:48.033 --> 00:04:49.533
bǐrúshuō běijīng de
比如说北京的
For example, Beijing's.

00:04:49.533 --> 00:04:51.300
bǐrúshuō shànghǎi de
比如说上海的
For example, Shanghai's.

00:04:51.300 --> 00:04:53.933
nǐ zhège xuésheng shì bǎ huàtí liáo méi le
你这个 student 是把话题聊没了
This student of yours ended the topic.

00:04:53.933 --> 00:04:55.133
tā huídá nǐ le
他回答你了
He answered you.

00:04:55.166 --> 00:04:56.733
ránhòu lǎoshī yào jìxùwèn
然后老师要继续问
And then the teacher has to continue asking.

00:04:56.733 --> 00:04:57.633
rúguǒ yíge
如果一个
If a.

00:04:57.633 --> 00:04:59.900
 bútài dǒng de nàge lǎoshī dehuà
不太懂的那个老师的话
Teacher who doesn't understand much.

00:05:00.033 --> 00:05:02.133
tā kěnéng zhège huàtí yě jiù jiéshù le
他可能这个话题也就结束了
He might just end the topic here.

00:05:02.266 --> 00:05:03.666
wǒ shuō de nàyàng de xuésheng
我说的那样的学生
The kind of student I'm talking about.

00:05:03.666 --> 00:05:05.800
tā tōngguò zhège jīhuì
他通过这个机会
He uses this opportunity.

00:05:05.800 --> 00:05:06.733
tā huì duō liàn
他会多练
He will practice more.

00:05:06.733 --> 00:05:08.133
tā huì shuō hěn duō huà
他会说很多话
He will say many words.

00:05:08.133 --> 00:05:11.133
wǒ fāxiàn hěn duō hànyǔ shuōde hǎo de xuésheng
我发现很多汉语说的好的学生
I found that many students who speak Chinese well.

00:05:11.133 --> 00:05:12.933
tāmen yǒu yíge gòngxìng
他们有一个共性
They have a commonality.

00:05:12.933 --> 00:05:14.266
gòngtóng de tèdiǎn
共同的特点
A common characteristic.

00:05:14.266 --> 00:05:15.633
jiùshì àishuō
就是爱说
Is loving to speak.

00:05:15.666 --> 00:05:17.133
duì （wǒ） jīngcháng shuō wǒde xuésheng
对 （我）经常说我的学生
Right, I often say to my students.

00:05:17.133 --> 00:05:17.966
búshì àishuō
不是爱说
Not just loving to speak.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:19.700
wǒ shuō "nǐmen tài pín le"
我说"你们太贫了"
I say, "You are too talkative."

00:05:19.700 --> 00:05:20.433
ò zhège shì
哦这个是
Oh, this is.

00:05:20.433 --> 00:05:21.466
shì Běijīnghuà
是北京话
Is Beijing dialect.

00:05:21.466 --> 00:05:22.500
duì "pín"
对  "贫"
Right, "pin."

00:05:22.533 --> 00:05:23.133
"pín" de yìsi
"贫"的意思
The meaning of "pin."

00:05:23.133 --> 00:05:24.800
búshì pínqióng
不是贫穷
Is not poverty.

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:25.700
pínkǔ de yìsi
贫苦的意思
The meaning of miserable.

00:05:25.700 --> 00:05:26.233
zàizhè
在这
In here.

00:05:26.266 --> 00:05:29.266
zhège "pín" jiùshì tài néng shuō le
这个"贫"就是太能说了
This "pin" means being too able to talk.

00:05:29.266 --> 00:05:31.066
jiùshì shuōde huà tàiduō le
就是说的话太多了
Meaning talking too much.

00:05:31.066 --> 00:05:32.033
méiyǒu huàtí
没有话题
Without a topic.

00:05:32.033 --> 00:05:33.333
huì zhǎo huàtí shuō
会找话题说
Will find topics to talk about.

00:05:33.333 --> 00:05:35.466
qíshí xué yǔyán xūyào zhèyàng
其实学语言需要这样
Actually, learning a language needs this.

00:05:35.466 --> 00:05:36.266
shìde èn
是的 嗯
Yes, um.

00:05:36.300 --> 00:05:38.466
suǒyǐ wǒ zài jiāo wǒ de xuésheng de shíhou
所以我在教我的学生的时候
So when I am teaching my students.

00:05:38.466 --> 00:05:40.733
wǒ zài gěi wǒ de xuésheng shàngkè de shíhou
我在给我的学生上课的时候
When I am giving lessons to my students.

00:05:40.733 --> 00:05:44.100
wǒ bù yǔnxǔ tāmen zhǐ huídá yíge zì
我不允许他们只回答一个字
I don't allow them to only answer one word.

00:05:44.100 --> 00:05:45.466
huòzhě liǎngge zì
或者两个字
Or two words.

00:05:45.500 --> 00:05:48.266
bǐrúshuō xǐhuan huòzhě bùxǐhuan
比如说喜欢或者不喜欢
For example, "like" or "dislike."

00:05:48.266 --> 00:05:49.933
duì huòzhě búduì
对或者不对
"Correct" or "incorrect."

00:05:49.966 --> 00:05:52.266
shì huòzhě búshì
是或者不是
"Yes" or "no."

00:05:52.266 --> 00:05:55.300
wǒ huì ràng tāmen huídá yíge wánzhěng de jùzi
我会让他们回答一个完整的句子
I will make them answer a full sentence.

00:05:55.333 --> 00:05:56.133
duì
对
Right.

00:05:56.133 --> 00:05:57.400
tāmen shuō lǎoshī
他们说老师
They say, "Teacher."

00:05:57.400 --> 00:05:58.700
nà wǒ zài shēnghuó zhōng
那我在生活中
"Then in real life."

00:05:58.700 --> 00:06:01.433
wǒ yě xūyào huídá yíge wánzhěng de jùzi ma
我也需要回答一个完整的句子吗
"Do I also need to answer with a full sentence?"

00:06:02.266 --> 00:06:03.833
shì yīnwèi shàngkè de shíhou
是因为上课的时候
It's because during class.

00:06:03.866 --> 00:06:07.766
wǒ xiǎng bāng tāmen liànxí tāmen de yǔgǎn hé yǔxù
我想帮他们练习他们的语感和语序
I want to help them practice their language sense and word order.

00:06:07.766 --> 00:06:10.600
rúguǒ tāmen jīngcháng shuō shì huòzhě búshì
如果他们经常说是或者不是
If they often say "yes" or "no."

00:06:10.633 --> 00:06:12.800
hěnshǎo shuō yíge wánzhěng de jùzi
很少说一个完整的句子
And rarely say a full sentence.

00:06:12.800 --> 00:06:14.733
nà tāmen zài shēnghuó zhōng
那他们在生活中
Then, in their daily lives.

00:06:14.733 --> 00:06:15.566
huòzhě zài tāmen
或者在他们
Or when they.

00:06:15.566 --> 00:06:18.166
bìxū shuō yíge wánzhěng de jùzi de shíhou
必须说一个完整的句子的时候
Must speak a complete sentence.

00:06:18.200 --> 00:06:19.466
tāmen jiù huì fàncuò
他们就会犯错
They will make mistakes.

00:06:19.466 --> 00:06:20.266
duì
对
Right.

00:06:20.266 --> 00:06:23.133
yīnwèi tāmen bùzhīdào zhège de yǔxù shì shénme
因为他们不知道这个的语序是什么
Because they don't know what the word order is.

00:06:23.133 --> 00:06:24.200
tāmen kěnéng shuō
他们可能说
They might say.

00:06:24.200 --> 00:06:24.900
"wǒ fàn chī"
"我饭吃"
"I meal eat."

00:06:24.900 --> 00:06:26.666
dàn qíshí wǒmen shuōde shì "wǒ chīfàn"
但其实我们说的是"我吃饭"
But actually we say "I eat meal."

00:06:26.700 --> 00:06:27.600
duì duìba
对 对吧
Right, right?

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:29.066
zhè zhǐshì yíge jiǎndān de lìzi
这只是一个简单的例子
This is just a simple example.

00:06:29.066 --> 00:06:30.600
nà gèng fùzá de lìzi
那更复杂的例子
Then for more complex examples.

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:33.666
tāmen kěnéng huì fàn yìxiē yǔxù shang de cuòwù
他们可能会犯一些语序上的错误
They might make some mistakes in word order.

00:06:33.666 --> 00:06:36.266
jiùshì tā huì bǎ nàge yǔfǎ
就是他会把那个语法
That is, he will take that grammar.

00:06:36.266 --> 00:06:38.833
shuōchéng shì yīngwén de yǔfǎ
说成是英文的语法
And speak it as English grammar.

00:06:38.900 --> 00:06:41.066
"wǒ chīfàn le zuótiān wǎnshang"
"我吃饭了昨天晚上"
"I ate meal yesterday evening."

00:06:41.066 --> 00:06:43.800
nà qíshí zhège kěnéng zhōngguórén yě tīngdedǒng
那其实这个可能中国人也听得懂
Actually, Chinese people might also understand this.

00:06:43.833 --> 00:06:46.866
dànshì jiù juéde yǒudiǎn qíguài a
但是就觉得有点奇怪啊
But it just feels a bit strange.

00:06:46.866 --> 00:06:47.866
shìde shìde
是的是的是
Yes, yes.

00:06:47.933 --> 00:06:50.600
suǒyǐ tèbié shì zài shàngkè de shíhou
所以特别是在上课的时候
So especially during class.

00:06:50.633 --> 00:06:52.666
rúguǒ nǐ yǒu jīhuì dehuà
如果你有机会的话
If you have the chance.

00:06:52.666 --> 00:06:53.733
nǐ jiù duōshuō
你就多说
You should speak more.

00:06:53.733 --> 00:06:54.266
duì èn
对嗯
Right, um.

00:06:54.266 --> 00:06:56.433
nǐ huídá lǎoshī de wánzhěng de jùzi
你回答老师的完整的句子
You answer the teacher with complete sentences.

00:06:56.433 --> 00:06:58.266
zhège búshì zài làngfèi shíjiān
这个不是在浪费时间
This is not wasting time.

00:06:58.266 --> 00:06:59.900
zhège shì zài bāngzhù nǐ zìjǐ
这个是在帮助你自己
This is helping yourself.

00:06:59.900 --> 00:07:01.600
zhǎodào yíge hànyǔ de yǔgǎn
找到一个汉语的语感
To find a sense for the Chinese language.

00:07:01.600 --> 00:07:03.333
duì yǔyán fāngmiàn
对 语言方面
Right, regarding language.

00:07:03.333 --> 00:07:06.200
lǎoshī shì xǐhuan "pín" de xuésheng de
老师是喜欢"贫"的学生的
Teachers like "talkative" students.

00:07:06.200 --> 00:07:08.700
shìde yīnwèi zhège yě shì zài bāng tāmen liànxí
是的 因为这个也是在帮他们练习
Yes, because this is also helping them practice.

00:07:08.733 --> 00:07:12.266
nǐ búdàn yào huídá yíge wánzhěng de jùzi
你不但要回答一个完整的句子
You not only need to answer with a complete sentence.

00:07:12.300 --> 00:07:15.600
nǐ háiyào zài kuòzhǎn shuō gèngduō de nèiróng
你还要再扩展说更多的内容
You also need to expand and say more content.

00:07:15.600 --> 00:07:16.933
xiàng Lìróng shuōde
像丽蓉说的
Like Lirong said.

00:07:16.933 --> 00:07:19.133
wǒ shì shénme shíhou chī guo de zhège cài
我是什么时候吃过的这个菜
When did I eat this dish?

00:07:19.133 --> 00:07:20.100
shì shénmecài ne
是什么菜呢
What kind of dish was it?

00:07:20.133 --> 00:07:20.933
Sìchuāncài ne
四川菜呢
Sichuan food?

00:07:20.933 --> 00:07:22.200
háishì Běijīngcài ne
还是北京菜呢
Or Beijing food?

00:07:22.200 --> 00:07:25.633
nà nǐ dìyīcì chī zhōngguócài shì shénme shíhou
那你第一次吃中国菜是什么时候
Then when was the first time you ate Chinese food?

00:07:25.633 --> 00:07:27.433
nǐ juéde zhōngguócài
你觉得中国菜
What do you think of Chinese food.

00:07:27.433 --> 00:07:30.466
gēn nǐmen guójiā de cài yǒu shénme bù yíyàng
跟你们国家的菜有什么不一样
Compared to the food in your country, what is different?

00:07:30.500 --> 00:07:32.200
ránhòu jiàgé zěnmeyàng
然后价格怎么样
And how was the price?

00:07:32.200 --> 00:07:34.133
qíshí dōukěyǐ shuō
其实都可以说
Actually, all of these can be said.

00:07:34.133 --> 00:07:38.600
bǎ suǒyǒude nǐ xuéguo de cí hé yǔfǎ dōu yòngshang
把所有的你学过的词和语法都用上
Use all the words and grammar you have learned.

00:07:38.633 --> 00:07:42.733
zhèyàng cáihuì qǐdào yíge liànxí de zuòyòng
这样才会起到一个练习的作用
Only in this way will it serve as practice.

00:07:42.733 --> 00:07:44.966
duì qíshí rúguǒ tā shuōbúdào dehuà
对 其实如果他说不到的话
Right, actually if he can't think of what to say.

00:07:45.000 --> 00:07:46.466
ránhòu tā diǎndào nàge huàtí
然后他点到那个话题
And then he mentions that topic.

00:07:46.466 --> 00:07:49.000
lǎoshī yěhuì yǐndǎo tā wǎng nàge fāngxiàng zǒu
老师也会引导他往那个方向走
The teacher will also guide him to go in that direction.

00:07:49.000 --> 00:07:51.066
bǐrúshuō shì yíge sānsìjí de xuésheng
比如说是一个三四级的学生
For example, a level three or four student.

00:07:51.066 --> 00:07:53.766
dāngrán lǎoshī chúle shuō nǐ xǐhuan chī zhōngguócài ma
当然老师除了说你喜欢吃中国菜吗
Of course, besides the teacher saying "do you like eating Chinese food?".

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:55.066
tā huídá xǐhuan
他回答喜欢
He answers "like."

00:07:55.066 --> 00:07:56.600
nà nǐ xǐhuan chī nǎlǐ de
那你喜欢吃哪里的
Then which place's food do you like to eat?

00:07:56.600 --> 00:07:57.433
nǎlǐ de cài
哪里的菜
Food from where?

00:07:57.433 --> 00:07:59.000
yǒu shénme tèdiǎn
有什么特点
What are the characteristics?

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:00.166
zhèxiē lǎoshī dōuhuì
这些老师都会
The teacher will do all of these.

00:08:00.200 --> 00:08:01.366
jiùshì gěitā
就是给他
Just for him.

00:08:01.366 --> 00:08:03.066
jiùshì yǐndǎo tā shuō chūlái
就是引导他说出来
Just guide him to say it.

00:08:03.100 --> 00:08:04.233
èn shì
嗯是
Um, yes.

00:08:04.266 --> 00:08:06.300
nà zài wǒmen gāng kāishǐ shuō de shíhou
那在我们刚开始说的时候
Then when we first started talking.

00:08:06.300 --> 00:08:09.100
wǒmen shuō liàn hěn zhòngyào duìbuduì
我们说练很重要对不对
We said practice is very important, right?

00:08:09.166 --> 00:08:11.633
nà wǒ juéde fēi zhuānyè de lǎoshī
那我觉得非专业的老师
Then I think non-professional teachers.

00:08:11.633 --> 00:08:14.133
tā dìyī tā kěnéng bùzhīdào zěnme jiāo
他第一他可能不知道怎么教
First, he might not know how to teach.

00:08:14.166 --> 00:08:14.966
dì'èr
第二
Second.

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:17.433
tā bùzhīdào zěnme liàn
他不知道怎么练
He doesn't know how to practice.

00:08:17.433 --> 00:08:19.466
qíshí qù yǐndǎo xuésheng
其实去引导学生
Actually, to guide students.

00:08:19.500 --> 00:08:20.866
qù bāngzhù xuésheng liànxí
去帮助学生练习
To help students practice.

00:08:20.866 --> 00:08:22.800
zhège shì hěn guānjiàn de yìdiǎn
这个是很关键的一点
This is a very key point.

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:24.533
yǒu yìxiē méiyǒu jīngyàn de lǎoshī
有一些没有经验的老师
There are some inexperienced teachers.

00:08:24.533 --> 00:08:27.733
tāmen zài jiǎng yì běn shū de shíhou huì jiǎng de hěn kuài
他们在讲一本书的时候会讲的很快
When they are teaching a book, they will teach very fast.

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:31.366
yīnwèi tāmen búhuì fǎnfù de bāng xuésheng liànxí
因为他们不会反复的帮学生练习
Because they won't repeatedly help students practice.

00:08:31.400 --> 00:08:33.533
tāmen bùdǒng zěnme qù liànxí
他们不懂怎么去练习
They don't understand how to practice.

00:08:33.533 --> 00:08:34.266
tāmen jiùhuì
他们就会
They will just.

00:08:34.266 --> 00:08:36.100
jiùshì zhuījìndù
就是追进度
Just chase the progress.

00:08:36.100 --> 00:08:38.100
jiùshì shuō zhèduàn shíjiān wǒ bǎ zhège shū jiǎngwán le
就是说这段时间我把这个书讲完了
Meaning, "I finished teaching this book in this period of time."

00:08:38.100 --> 00:08:39.266
wánle jiù wánle
完了就完了
When it's finished, it's just finished.

00:08:39.266 --> 00:08:42.133
wǒ juéde jiù xiàng húlúntūnzǎo
我觉得就像囫囵吞枣
I think it's like swallowing a date whole (without chewing).

00:08:42.133 --> 00:08:43.233
jiùshì chījìnqù le
就是吃进去了
It's just eaten.

00:08:43.233 --> 00:08:45.100
ránhòu jiù shénme gǎnjué méiyǒu
然后就什么感觉没有
And then there is no feeling at all.

00:08:45.100 --> 00:08:46.933
ránhòu qíshí duì xuésheng láishuō
