shàngkè de shíhou liànxí de shíjiān shì yǒuxiànde
上课的时候练习的时间是有限的
Practice time during class is limited.

00:09:49.600 --> 00:09:51.866
bùguǎn shì yīduìyī de kè háishì bānjíkè
不管是一对一的课还是班级课
Whether it's a one-on-one class or a group class.

00:09:51.866 --> 00:09:54.566
liànxí de shíjiān dōu bǐjiào yǒuxiàn
练习的时间都比较有限
The practice time is relatively limited.

