00:10:32.600 --> 00:10:35.366
qíshí rúguǒ nǐ xiǎng yǒu jīhuì dehuà
其实如果你想有机会的话
Actually, if you want to have opportunities.

00:10:35.400 --> 00:10:36.833
jīhuì háishì hěnduō de
机会还是很多的
There are still many opportunities.

