tāmen dōu hěn xǐhuan liáotiān
他们都很喜欢聊天
They all like chatting very much.

00:10:45.066 --> 00:10:46.600
nǐ kěyǐ gēn tāmen liáo
你可以跟他们聊
You can chat with them.

