00:12:30.933 --> 00:12:33.300
nà tā kěndìng shì zhēnduì nǐde nénglì
那他肯定是针对你的能力
Then it must be targeted at your ability.

00:12:33.333 --> 00:12:34.800
huòzhě yǔyán xíguàn
