Right, that's just a single sentence.

00:21:49.466 --> 00:21:51.533
ránhòu ne hái kěyǐ xiě yí duàn huà
然后呢 还可以写一段话
Furthermore, you can write a short paragraph.

00:21:51.533 --> 00:21:54.900
jiùshì yòng zhè yíkè suǒyǒude cí xiě yíduànhuà
就是用这一课所有的词写一段话
Specifically, use all the words from this lesson to write a passage.

00:21:54.900 --> 00:21:57.533
bǐrúshuō jīntiān de tiānqì hěnhǎo
比如说今天的天气很好
For example: "Today's weather is very good."

00:21:57.533 --> 00:21:58.966
shì qíngtiān
