00:21:58.966 --> 00:21:59.900
suǒyǐ
所以
"So..."

00:21:59.933 --> 00:22:03.800
wǒ gēn wǒde péngyou yìqǐ qù wàimiàn tī zúqiú le
我跟我的朋友一起去外面踢足球了
"...I went outside to play soccer with my friends."

00:22:03.800 --> 00:22:06.666
wǒmen tī le yíge xiǎoshí
我们踢了一个小时
"We played for an hour."

00:22:06.733 --> 00:22:08.200
tī wán qiú yǐhòu
踢完球以后
"After playing soccer..."

00:22:08.233 --> 00:22:09.600
wǒmen hěn lèi
我们很累
"...we were very tired."

00:22:09.666 --> 00:22:13.900
suǒyǐ wǒmen yìqǐ qù fànguǎn chīfàn le
所以我们一起去饭馆吃饭了
"So we went to a restaurant to eat together."

00:22:13.933 --> 00:22:14.866
wǒmen chī le
我们吃了
"We ate..."

00:22:14.866 --> 00:22:15.266
...
...
...

00:22:15.266 --> 00:22:16.666
shénme fàn dāngrán
什么饭当然
"...some food. Of course..."

00:22:16.666 --> 00:22:19.000
zhège hòumiàn de zhèxiē nèiróng
这个后面的这些内容
"...all this content following it..."

00:22:19.000 --> 00:22:21.933
dōu yīnggāi shì nǐ yǐqián xué guo
都应该是你以前学过
...should be things you've already learned.

00:22:22.033 --> 00:22:24.200
yīnwèi zài yíge xīn de kèlǐ
因为在一个新的课里
Because in a new lesson.

00:22:24.200 --> 00:22:26.866
nǐ bùnéng xuéxí tàiduō de shēngcí
你不能学习太多的生词
You can't handle too many new words at once.

00:22:26.866 --> 00:22:30.233
nǐ de shēngcí zhǐ néng shì gēn zhège tiānqì yǒuguān de
你的生词只能是跟这个天气有关的
The new words should only be the ones related to the weather.

00:22:30.266 --> 00:22:32.466
nà biéde kěyǐ liànxí de cí
那别的可以练习的词
The other words used for practice.

00:22:32.500 --> 00:22:34.133
dōushì nǐ yǐjīng xué guo de
都是你已经学过的
Should all be words you already know.

00:22:34.133 --> 00:22:35.833
zhèyàng de huà nǐ jiù bú huì tài lèi
这样的话你就不会太累
This way, you won't get too exhausted.

00:22:35.833 --> 00:22:39.266
suǒyǐ qíshí nǐ liànxí yícì
所以其实你练习一次
So, in fact, practicing once...

00:22:39.266 --> 00:22:40.733
búyào yòng tàiduō de cí
不要用太多的词
Don't use too many words.

00:22:40.733 --> 00:22:43.066
bǐrúshuō wǔ ge shēngcí huòzhě zěnmeyàng
比如说50个生词或者怎么样
For example, 50 new words or something like that.

00:22:43.066 --> 00:22:45.133
zhège wǒ juéde méiyǒu tài hǎo de xiàoguǒ
这个我觉得没有太好的效果
I don't think that would be very effective.

00:22:45.133 --> 00:22:47.666
kěnéng yícì yòng shí ge shēngcí
可能一次用10个生词
Maybe use 10 new words at a time.

00:22:47.666 --> 00:22:48.600
ránhòu ne
然后呢
And then.

00:22:48.600 --> 00:22:52.900
qù yòng yǐqián xuéguo de yìxiē cí yìqǐ liànxí
去用以前学过的一些词一起练习
Practice them together with words you've learned before.

00:22:52.900 --> 00:22:54.500
gēn zhè shí ge cí yìqǐ liànxí
跟这10个词一起练习
Practice using them with those 10 words.

00:22:54.500 --> 00:22:56.700
wǒ juéde zhèyàng de xiàoguǒ huì bǐjiào hǎo
我觉得这样的效果会比较好
I think this will have better results.

00:22:56.700 --> 00:22:58.333
búdàn liànxí le yǐqián de cí
不但练习了以前的词
Not only do you practice old words.

00:22:58.333 --> 00:23:00.600
érqiě ne xuéxí le yìxiē xīn de cí
而且呢学习了一些新的词
But you also learn some new ones.

00:23:00.600 --> 00:23:02.200
duì duì zhèyàng ne
对对这样呢
Right, and in this way.

00:23:02.200 --> 00:23:03.966
jiù huì fùxí dào yǐqián de cí
就会复习到以前的词
You'll get to review the old words.

00:23:04.000 --> 00:23:06.700
ránhòu yòu liǎojiě le xiànzài xīn de cí
然后又了解了现在新的词
And also become familiar with the new words.

00:23:06.700 --> 00:23:09.233
ránhòu xiàcì zài bǎ zhège xīnde cí
然后下次再把这个新的词
Then next time, take these new words.

00:23:09.233 --> 00:23:10.600
dàngzuò yǐqián xuéguo de cí
当做以前学过的词
Treat them as words you've already learned.

00:23:10.600 --> 00:23:11.800
zài fǎnfù liànxí
再反复练习
And practice them repeatedly.

00:23:11.800 --> 00:23:15.366
ránhòu zhèyàng yìdiǎn yìdiǎn de jiāshēn nǐde jìyì
然后这样一点一点的加深你的记忆
And bit by bit, this deepens your memory.

00:23:15.600 --> 00:23:17.300
duì rúguǒ nǐde yǔbàn
对 如果你的语伴
Right, and if your language partner.

00:23:17.300 --> 00:23:20.233
nǐmen gāng kāishǐ yìqǐ liànxí huòzhě xuéxí
你们刚开始一起练习或者学习
And you've just started practicing or studying together.

00:23:20.233 --> 00:23:22.666
tā bù zhīdào nǐ huì shénme cí
他不知道你会什么词
They don't know which words you know.

00:23:22.666 --> 00:23:24.433
nǐ kěyǐ xiě xiàlái gěi tā
你可以写下来给他
You can write them down for them.

00:23:24.433 --> 00:23:26.133
nǐ gàosu tā wǒ huì zhèxiē cí
你告诉他我会这些词
Tell them, "I know these words."

00:23:26.133 --> 00:23:28.466
nà nǐ jiù yòng zhèxiē cí gēn wǒ liànxí
那你就用这些词跟我练习
"So please use these words to practice with me."

00:23:28.466 --> 00:23:29.533
wǒ huì zhèxiē yǔfǎ
我会这些语法
"I know these grammar points."

00:23:29.533 --> 00:23:31.466
nǐ yòng zhèxiē yǔfǎ gēnwǒ liànxí
你用这些语法跟我练习
"Use this grammar to practice with me."

00:23:31.466 --> 00:23:32.800
zhèshì yíge fāngfǎ
这是一个方法
That's one way.

00:23:32.833 --> 00:23:35.900
nà rúguǒ nǐde yǔbàn tā gēnnǐ shúxi yǐhòu ne
那如果你的语伴他跟你熟悉以后呢
Once your language partner becomes familiar with you.

00:23:35.900 --> 00:23:37.533
kěnéng zài tā de nǎozi li
可能在他的脑子里
