00:24:13.700 --> 00:24:16.066
nǐ kěyǐ zài xiàmiàn gēn wǒmen fēnxiǎng nǐ de fāngfǎ
你可以在下面跟我们分享你的方法
You can share your methods with us in the comments.

00:24:16.066 --> 00:24:17.700
wǒmen yě kěyǐ jièjiàn yíxià
我们也可以借鉴一下
We can learn from them.

00:24:17.700 --> 00:24:19.800
ránhòu yě kěyǐ fēnxiǎng gěi wǒmen de xuésheng
然后也可以分享给我们的学生
And share them with our students.

00:24:19.800 --> 00:24:20.400
duì
对
Exactly.

00:24:20.400 --> 00:24:22.866
dāng nǐ bǎ zhège jùzi liànshú le yǐhòu ne
当你把这个句子练熟了以后呢
Once you've practiced a sentence until you're fluent.

00:24:22.866 --> 00:24:24.600
nǐ zài qù gēntā zuò duìhuà
你再去跟他做对话
Then you can start a dialogue with them.

00:24:24.600 --> 00:24:26.466
ránhòu zài zuò gèngshēn de jiāoliú
然后再做更深的交流
And then have deeper conversations.

00:24:26.466 --> 00:24:27.400
duì shì zhèyàng de
对 是这样的
Yes, that's how it is.

00:24:27.433 --> 00:24:29.700
zhèxiē nián jiàole zhème duō xuésheng
这些年教了这么多学生
I've taught so many students over the years.

00:24:29.700 --> 00:24:31.833
wǒ fāxiàn hěnduō xuésheng
我发现很多学生
I've noticed that many students.

00:24:31.833 --> 00:24:35.000
xuédào HSKsì jiù fàngqì le
学到HSK4就放弃了
Give up once they reach HSK 4.

00:24:35.066 --> 00:24:39.133
shì yīnwèi cóng HSKyī dào HSKsì
是因为从HSK1到HSK4
It's because from HSK 1 to HSK 4.

00:24:39.133 --> 00:24:42.600
dōu shì shēnghuózhōng chángcháng huì yòngdào de yìxiē cí
都是生活中常常会用到的一些词
