00:24:42.600 --> 00:24:44.400
duì hěn kǒuyǔ de cí
对 很口语的词
Yes, very colloquial words.

00:24:44.400 --> 00:24:45.633
bǐjiào hǎokǎo
比较好考
They are relatively easy to test for.

00:24:45.633 --> 00:24:46.100
duì
对
Right.

00:24:46.133 --> 00:24:49.000
ránhòu ne yīnwèi nǐ zài shēnghuózhōng huì chángcháng yòngdào
然后呢因为你在生活中会常常用到
And since you use them often in daily life.

00:24:49.000 --> 00:24:50.900
nǐ yě huì bǐjiào róngyì jìzhù
你也会比较容易记住
They are easier to remember.

00:24:50.900 --> 00:24:51.500
duì
对
Yes.

00:24:51.500 --> 00:24:55.566
yǒude xuésheng kěnéng juéde wǒ xuédào HSKsì jiù gòule
有的学生可能觉得我学到HSK4就够了
Some students might feel that HSK 4 is enough.

00:24:55.566 --> 00:24:56.200
huòzhě ne
或者呢
Or else.

00:24:56.233 --> 00:24:59.866
tāmen huì juéde HSKwǔ hé liù tài nán le
他们会觉得HSK5和6太难了
They feel HSK 5 and 6 are too difficult.

00:24:59.866 --> 00:25:00.933
wǒ xué bu xiàqù le
我学不下去了
"I can't go on studying."

00:25:00.933 --> 00:25:02.433
suǒyǐ wǒ yào fàngqì
所以我要放弃
"So I'm going to give up."

00:25:02.433 --> 00:25:03.166
nà wǒ zhīdào
那我知道
Well, I know.

00:25:03.200 --> 00:25:05.833
Lìróng jīngcháng jiāo HSKwǔ hé liù
丽蓉经常教HSK5和6
Lirong often teaches HSK 5 and 6.

00:25:05.833 --> 00:25:07.500
bāngzhù nǐde xuésheng kǎoshì
帮助你的学生考试
Helping your students with the exams.

00:25:07.500 --> 00:25:10.000
zài zhè fāngmiàn nǐ bǐjiào yǒu jīngyàn
在这方面你比较有经验
You are quite experienced in this area.

00:25:10.000 --> 00:25:11.933
nǐ kěyǐ gēn wǒmen fēnxiǎng yíxià nǐde jīngyàn ma
你可以跟我们分享一下你的经验吗
Could you share some of your experience with us?

00:25:11.933 --> 00:25:13.100
èn hǎode hǎode
嗯好的好的
Mm, sure, sure.

00:25:13.100 --> 00:25:14.800
yīnwèi quèshí
因为确实
Because indeed.

00:25:14.833 --> 00:25:17.033
( HSK ) sì gēn wǔ huòzhě wǔ dào liù
(HSK)4跟5或者5到6
The jump from 4 to 5 or 5 to 6.

00:25:17.033 --> 00:25:19.233
dōushì yíge hěn bù yíyàng de
都是一个很不一样的
Is a very different level.

00:25:19.266 --> 00:25:21.233
jiùshì nèixiē cí jiùshì wánquán bù yíyàng
就是那些词就是完全不一样
The vocabulary is completely different.

00:25:21.233 --> 00:25:22.066
xiàng nǐ shuō de
像你说的
Like you said.

00:25:22.066 --> 00:25:24.100
sìjí zhīqián dōushì wǒmen chángyòng de
四级之前都是我们常用的
Before level 4, it's all commonly used words.

00:25:24.100 --> 00:25:26.000
wǒmen kǎoshì de shíhou jiù xiāngduì róngyì
我们考试的时候就相对容易
So the exams are relatively easy.

00:25:26.000 --> 00:25:29.066
hěn duō xuésheng cóng kǎo yījí dào sìjí hěn zìxìn
很多学生从考一级到四级很自信
Many students are very confident from level 1 to level 4.

00:25:29.066 --> 00:25:30.066
ránhòu guò le
然后过了
And they pass.

00:25:30.066 --> 00:25:31.800
ránhòu kǎo de fēn yě bù dī
然后考的分也不低
And their scores aren't low either.

00:25:31.800 --> 00:25:34.433
nà dào kǎo wǔjí de shíhou jiù hěn shīwàng
那到考五级的时候就很失望
But then they are very disappointed when they take level 5.

00:25:34.433 --> 00:25:35.933
wèishénme chà zhème duō
为什么差这么多
"Why is there such a big difference?"

00:25:35.933 --> 00:25:39.633
nàshì yīnwèi quèshí shì wǔjí liùjí de shíhou
那是因为确实是五级六级的时候
That's because for level 5 and level 6.

00:25:39.633 --> 00:25:41.500
tāmen nèixiē cí jiù gèng nán le
他们那些词就更难了
Those words are much harder.

00:25:41.500 --> 00:25:45.133
huòzhě shì wǒmen rìcháng shēnghuózhōng bútài shuō de
或者是我们日常生活中不太说的
Or they are words we don't say much in daily life.

00:25:45.300 --> 00:25:47.400
jiùxiàng wǒmen pǔtōng de zhōngguórén
就像我们普通的中国人
Even for us ordinary Chinese people.

00:25:47.400 --> 00:25:48.500
zài liáotiān de shíhou
在聊天的时候
When chatting.

00:25:48.500 --> 00:25:51.333
yě hěnnán shuōdào wǔjí liùjí de nàge cíhuì
也很难说到五级六级的那个词汇
It's hard to use that level 5 or 6 vocabulary.

00:25:51.333 --> 00:25:53.833
wǒ zài péixùn tāmen wǔjí liùjí de shíhou
我在培训他们五级六级的时候
When I train them for level 5 and 6.

00:25:53.833 --> 00:25:56.500
shǒuxiān yàozuò de qíshì shì sǐ bànfǎ
首先要做的其实是死办法
